---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

---

<Layout 
  title="Cookie Policy | SwankyBoyz" 
  description="Learn how SwankyBoyz uses cookies and tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience and improve our services."
  noindex={false}
>
  <main class="bg-charcoal py-24">
    <article class="container max-w-4xl space-y-8">
      <header class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-champagne/80">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl leading-tight text-off-white sm:text-5xl">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-off-white/70">
          Understanding how we use cookies and similar technologies to improve your experience on SwankyBoyz.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-off-white/80">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">What Are Cookies?</h2>
          <p>
            Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device when you visit a website. They help websites remember your preferences, enhance functionality, and provide analytics about site usage.
          </p>
          <p>
            We use cookies and similar technologies (such as local storage and pixels) to improve your experience on SwankyBoyz and to understand how our Site is used.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-off-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-off-white mb-2">Essential Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/70">
                <strong>Purpose:</strong> Required for basic site functionality and security
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/60">
                These cookies are necessary for the Site to function properly. They enable core features like page navigation, secure areas access, and form submissions. You cannot opt out of these cookies as they're essential for the Site to work.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-off-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-off-white mb-2">Analytics Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/70">
                <strong>Purpose:</strong> Help us understand how visitors use our Site
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/60">
                We use analytics services like Cloudflare Analytics and Google Analytics to collect anonymous information about page views, time on site, bounce rates, and traffic sources. This helps us improve our content and user experience.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/60 mt-2">
                <strong>You can opt out of these cookies</strong> through our cookie banner or browser settings.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-off-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-off-white mb-2">Preference Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/70">
                <strong>Purpose:</strong> Remember your settings and preferences
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/60">
                These cookies allow the Site to remember choices you make (such as your cookie preferences) and provide enhanced, personalized features.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-off-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-off-white mb-2">Affiliate Tracking Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/70">
                <strong>Purpose:</strong> Track affiliate referrals and commissions
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-off-white/60">
                When you click on affiliate links, cookies may be set by our affiliate partners (like Amazon) to track purchases and attribute commissions. These cookies don't personally identify you and are used solely for attribution purposes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Some cookies on our Site are set by third-party services we use:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Cloudflare Analytics:</strong> Website performance and security analytics</li>
            <li><strong>Amazon Associates:</strong> Affiliate link tracking and attribution</li>
            <li><strong>Social Media Platforms:</strong> Embedded content from Instagram, TikTok, etc.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            These third parties have their own privacy policies governing how they use cookies. We recommend reviewing their policies for more information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-off-white mb-2">Cookie Consent Banner</h3>
              <p>
                When you first visit SwankyBoyz, we display a cookie consent banner allowing you to accept or reject non-essential cookies. Your choice is saved and respected on future visits.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-off-white mb-2">Browser Settings</h3>
              <p>
                You can control and delete cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
                <li>View and delete existing cookies</li>
                <li>Block third-party cookies</li>
                <li>Block cookies from specific sites</li>
                <li>Block all cookies</li>
                <li>Delete all cookies when closing your browser</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-2">
                <strong>Note:</strong> Disabling cookies may affect the functionality and features of our Site.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-off-white mb-2">Opt-Out Links</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
                <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-champagne hover:text-champagne/80 transition underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Local Storage and Other Technologies</h2>
          <p>
            In addition to cookies, we may use:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Store data locally in your browser for improved performance</li>
            <li><strong>Session Storage:</strong> Temporary storage that's cleared when you close your browser</li>
            <li><strong>Pixels and Beacons:</strong> Small transparent images that help us track page views and user interactions</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            These technologies serve similar purposes to cookies and are managed through your browser settings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Cookie Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Different cookies have different lifespans:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Deleted when you close your browser</li>
            <li><strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> Remain until their expiration date (typically 30-365 days) or until you delete them</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Updates to This Cookie Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for legal, operational, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of material changes by updating the "Last Updated" date at the bottom of this page.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">More Information</h2>
          <p>
            For more details about how we collect and use your data, please read our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-champagne hover:text-champagne/80 transition underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you have questions about our use of cookies, contact us at:
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="mailto:privacy@swankyboyz.com" class="text-champagne hover:text-champagne/80 transition underline">privacy@swankyboyz.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-off-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-off-white/60">
            <strong class="text-off-white">Last Updated:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
